org.ow2.chameleon.metric.measure
Class ScalarMeasure.ScalarMeasureBuilder<Q extends Quantity<Q>>

java.lang.Object
  org.ow2.chameleon.metric.measure.ScalarMeasure.ScalarMeasureBuilder<Q>
Type Parameters:
Q - the kind of quantity captured by the measure
Enclosing class:
ScalarMeasure<Q extends Quantity<Q>>
public static class ScalarMeasure.ScalarMeasureBuilder<Q extends Quantity<Q>>
extends Object

Builder to create scalar measure object.

Examples:

     ScalarMeasure measure = new ScalarMeasure.ScalarMeasureBuilder()
          .sensor("thermometer")
          .hasMeasured(new Temperature(10, Temperature.CELSIUS))
          .at(new Date())
          .build();

     ScalarMeasure measure2 = new ScalarMeasure.ScalarMeasureBuilder()
          .measure(new Temperature(10, Temperature.CELSIUS))
          .takenBy("thermometer")
          .at(new Date())
          .build();
